OL,3,CTube strike ends but further
OL,4,Cindustrial action planned
OL,6,FTransport for London (TfL) continued
OL,7,Fto urge passengers to check before
OL,8,Fthey travel.
OL,10,FThe union, which is in dispute over
OL,11,Fchanges to the working week, is
OL,12,Fplanning four more 24-hour strikes in
OL,13,FMay and June unless the row is
OL,14,Fresolved.
OL,16,FPubs and restaurants in London fear
OL,17,Fthat this week's strikes will have a
OL,18,Fbig impact on their business.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
