CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776942175
OL,3,CTube strike ends but further
OL,4,Cindustrial action planned
OL,6,FRMT official Jared Wood said union
OL,7,Fmembers felt strongly about the issues
OL,8,Fat the heart of the dispute.
OL,10,FHe said the row was not just about a
OL,11,Ffour-day week, saying other issues
OL,12,Fwere involved such as the length of
OL,13,Fshifts and changes to annual leave.
OL,15,FHe said: "TfL need to come forward
OL,16,Fwith changes to their proposals for
OL,17,Fthis dispute to be resolved.
OL,19,F"There is absolute unanimity among our
OL,20,Fmembers that we have to fight these
OL,21,Fproposals."
OL,26,@wD@JOU{D@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
