PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1776942175
OL,3,CTube strike ends but further
OL,4,Cindustrial action planned
OL,6,FMr Wood said there was now "a lot of
OL,7,Fbad feeling" between the drivers and
OL,8,FLondon Underground.
OL,10,FSome bus routes in the capital
OL,11,Foperated by Stagecoach will be
OL,12,Faffected by a separate 24-hour strike
OL,13,Ffrom 5am on Friday.
OL,15,FClaire Mann, TfL's chief operating
OL,16,Fofficer, said: "We have set out
OL,17,Fproposals to the RMT for a four-day
OL,18,Fworking week.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@LO]xD@POU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
